item.title: CVE-2016-8730|2024-08-06T02:27:41.448Z -- corel -- corel%20photo-paint
item.description: An of bound write / memory corruption vulnerability exists in the GIF parsing functionality of Core PHOTO-PAINT X8 18.1.0.661. A specially crafted GIF file can cause a vulnerability resulting in potential memory corruption resulting in code execution. An attacker can send the victim a specific GIF file to trigger this vulnerability.
